text: Patrick le Rolland (born 15 May 1943) is a French equestrian. He competed in the individual dressage event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
